<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> yōrayaṁ bhīmaparākramōpi bhīmassadānaṁdakaraḥ prajānāṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> veṁggīśacālukyakulā
