<lb n="5" break="no"/>khaṇḍavarttiruciraṁ kāṁcīpurīpālakaḥ [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] svasti sarvvalōkāśraya śrīviṣṇuvarddhanamahārājula pravarddhamānavija
<lb n="6" break="no"/>yarājyasaṁvatsaramulu 4 gu śrāhi śakavarṣamulu 105<unclear>1</unclear> ṇḍagu nēṁṭi Uttarāyanasaṁkrāṁti nimittamuna maṇḍalika bo 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ddināyakuni tammuṇḍu bhīmināyakuṇḍu śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvarakuṁ beṭṭina yakhaṇḍavarttilōhadaṇḍu diviya
<lb n="8" break="no"/>lu 4 nālvunu dēvara kilaramuna nāvabōla sōmaṇḍunu peddibōla nāvaṇḍunu doḍḍana bādaṇḍunu nāvabōla prōla(ṁ)ṇḍu
