<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> bōla prōlani vasamuna niccina Inupayeḍlu 50 talarāsi nāvabōla prōlani yaḍapuna kāṭabōla <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
